items.title: First Steps
items.content_html:
Getting started with the Connector 365 Upgrade App

Here you will find all the important information and instructions on how to install the Connector 365 Upgrade App.

Simply use either the bottom or left navigation menu.

In case a question could not be answered, we are happy to help you personally. You can find the necessary contact information on the support page.
